⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Graendal
node WOT · WOT · ⟦Graendal:WOT:8024dd⟧

WHO   — Graendal — the hedonist who breaks minds
WHAT  — One of the Forsaken — a master of Compulsion who rules through enslaved thralls rather than open force.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the Shadow  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — She is the Shadow's most insidious hand — corruption that works through the minds of others, unseen.
HOW   — She weaves Compulsion to turn rulers, channelers, and Aes Sedai into adoring puppets, and rarely risks herself.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  She never lifts the blade — she makes you lift it for her, and smile.

